        </a>
        <h2>
            千年终结的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 3 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1231428">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1231428/" class="title-link">再见大师</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1231428"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ewine/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1077129-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ewine/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ewine</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-10-30"
      class="main-meta">2007-10-30 18:02:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1231428_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  遭遇德鲁克后，我有幸拜读到曼纽尔·卡斯特（Manuel Castells）的大作，获益终身。在经营自我和应对世界之上，这两位大师成为我最好的启蒙导师。直接来讲，德鲁克教给我的是个人管理，其核心是知识管理；卡斯特教给我的则是学会自我编程和自我创新以享受不确定。从思想或学术角...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1231428/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1231428_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1231428_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



